name: Soaked °_°
description:
SUMMER DAYS
Drenched in golden sunshine / 
Pouring down on us like a shower /
All we want to do is dance and run /
and jump and play /
In the grass, in the sea, in the air.

We feel so free and alive.
The world is ours to enjoy /
Every moment a delight.

In the company of friends /
We laugh and sing and tease.
The days just fly by.

How we wish summer could last forever.

Thank you, Nature, for this gift /

Of joy, peace, and happiness.

We appreciate you more than you know.
